Convention for stem naming: 

ASCAP-[WorkID]-[Title]-[Instrument]-[Index]

Examples: 

    ASCAP-123456-Glass Orchard-DRUMS-01.wav

    ASCAP-123456-Glass Orchard-BASS-01.wav

    ASCAP-123456-Glass Orchard-GTR-RHY-01.wav

Contributions that do not respect this convention will be REMOVED WITHOUT FURTHER COMMENT. - Seidkona
